snippet.title: Daemonologie Trailer
snippet.description:
My entry for the HPS1 Halloween Jam 2020. 
https://katanalevy.itch.io/daemonologie
Daemonologie is a short interactive experience where you play the role of a witch finder in a small Scottish village. Question the townsfolk and try to work out who the witch is. If they are not forthcoming you may employ other methods of persuassion. 
At the end of 5 days someone will hang, be sure in your choice!
